level.text: A certified nurse-midwife shall adhere to the standards set forth in the American College of Nurse Midwives’ “Code of Ethics” as they may be amended or republished from time to time.

level.heading: SOURCE
level.text: Final Rulemaking published at 36 DCR 3497, 3499 (May 12, 1989); as amended by Final Rulemaking published at 49 DCR 11751 (December 27, 2002); as amended by Final Rulemaking published at 51 DCR 7228 (July 23, 2004).
